{"tid":804464,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Windows 拜拜] 一半以上的遊戲能於 Linux 最新版 STEAM 穩定執行！","createTime":"2018-09-03T04:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T03:51:11.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"95887fdb7b84e3956ee989d9438f719c64cf353e","tid":804464,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:41:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/jasonevangelho/2018/08/27/steam-for-linux-adds-1000-perfectly-playable-windows-games-in-under-a-week/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fjasonevangelho%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2Fsteam-for-linux-adds-1000-perfectly-playable-windows-games-in-under-a-week%2F&d=hzNM7YY%2BVeW%2BoBM08pddXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=90e7c05f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/jasonevangelho/2018/08/27/steam-for-linux-adds-1000-perfectly-playable-windows-games-in-under-a-week/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://thumbor.forbes.com/thumbor/711x606/https://blogs-images.forbes.com/jasonevangelho/files/2018/08/27-more-whitelisted-1200x1023.jpg?width=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbor.forbes.com%2Fthumbor%2F711x606%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fblogs-images.forbes.com%2Fjasonevangelho%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F08%2F27-more-whitelisted-1200x1023.jpg%3Fwidth%3D960&h=9012be7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Valve has whitelisted only 27 games, but many more are perfectly playable.</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://thumbor.forbes.com/thumbor/711x437/https://blogs-images.forbes.com/jasonevangelho/files/2018/08/stability-snapshot-steam-play-1200x738.jpg?width=960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbor.forbes.com%2Fthumbor%2F711x437%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fblogs-images.forbes.com%2Fjasonevangelho%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F08%2Fstability-snapshot-steam-play-1200x738.jpg%3Fwidth%3D960&h=b7ab7fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">The current stability snapshot of Steam Play for Linux, based on more than 2000 Windows games tested.</span></div>"},{"pid":"122cb30cd5749b22edc6f45313ad0ed2551c99d2","tid":804464,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"Valve has officially whitelisted only 27 games at this early stage, but we can expect that number to grow at a rapid pace.<br />\n<br />\nAs of this writing, 2134 unique games have been user-tested from the Steam for Windows library. Each game receives one of six ratings: Completely Stable, Stable, Unstable, Unplayable, Crashes or Won&rsquo;t Start. A Completely Stable rating signifies that the game exhibits native-like performance with no bugs or errors. Since testing began, 971 unique titles have been stamped with a Completely Stable status.<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s worth pointing out that your mileage may vary depending on GPU driver version and operating system. Note that Ubuntu accounts for 37% of all submissions (Arch Linux is in 2nd place), and 64% of users are running on Nvidia."},{"pid":"1f2641f69fb1c3f8583897d24441b2da7bf6805c","tid":804464,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"用linux"},{"pid":"cc3b2904ba599e045c4c446babcaf5524deb2064","tid":804464,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:47:49.000Z","msg":"今次咁好題材又唔見A狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨係識入人地post講埋啲on99 離題野"},{"pid":"a28b41ae86f6f0c34b684241a6d6d594027f3433","tid":804464,"uid":14817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"開到同玩得順？<br />\n仲有如果隻驚run 唔到第三方會唔會support?"},{"pid":"aab785c5fbe55d21f7dc9423cb0615b90f0a020d","tid":804464,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"睇漏咗原來係2000幾隻遊戲當中有一半以上能穩定執行至