sual filters, like ambient occlusion.<br />\n(check the first minute of the video to see the settings)<br />\n<br />\nThe capturing software (obs) lowers the frame rate quite a bit,<br />\nwhen I stop the recording I get most often 60fps and average I would say 55 fps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n<br />\nCPU: i5-4690K slightly overclocked @4.2 GHz<br />\nGPU: gtx 980 Asus Strix<br />\nRAM: 16GB G.Skill TridentX 2133 MHz (2x8) PC3-17000<br />\nScreen: Benq XL2430T @120Hz<br />\n<br />\nDistro: Debian 8 Jessie with Gnome Shell.<br />\n<br />\nVideo captured with OBS + NVENC"},{"pid":"52496538c700f8b917806ea0839389c5883f3987","tid":804464,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51635d9693721fcb2ca0141d05ef41a1649b23f9","tid":804464,"uid":14817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aab785c5fbe55d21f7dc9423cb0615b90f0a020d","tid":804464,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"睇漏咗原來係2000幾隻遊戲當中有一半以上能穩定執行至啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"Linux就咁update steam 就得？<br />\n裝左雙系統 一陣就試全高GTA V <br />\n對比睇下fps"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"Steam beta 至玩得"},{"pid":"c4d29b38d5b273a4564e0ef54368ee2cf3a73fba","tid":804464,"uid":14817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52496538c700f8b917806ea0839389c5883f3987","tid":804464,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51635d9693721fcb2ca0141d05ef41a1649b23f9","tid":804464,"uid":14817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aab785c5fbe55d21f7dc9423cb0615b90f0a020d","tid":804464,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:51:34.000Z","msg":"睇漏咗原來係2000幾隻遊戲當中有一半以上能穩定執行至啱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:59:42.000Z","msg":"Linux就咁update steam 就得？<br />\n裝左雙系統 一陣就試全高GTA V <br />\n對比睇下fps"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"Steam beta 至玩得"},"citedBy":1,"replyT